RawLine: TNPC_60073008,婆婆，我看你就別繼續在村口等了，雖然還不清楚那人是誰，但來者不善，善者不來，這樣實在太危險。,婆婆，我看你就别继续在村口等了，虽然还不清楚那人是谁，但来者不善，善者不来，这样实在太危险。

Items.mt: Grandma, I think you should not continue to wait at the entrance of the village, although it is not clear who that person is, but those who come are not good and those who are good do not come, this is too dangerous.
